\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces Worked example ($N{=}2$, $\tau {=}3$). A toy log of four variants, the successor multisets its N-grams induce, and two generated shadow traces: a recombination of attested steps, and a Katz-consistent mutation ($e^{*}$) whose rate came from the resolved order-2 context and whose proposal came from the order-1 context.}}{12}{figure.1.4}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:example}{{4}{12}{Worked example ($N{=}2$, $\tau {=}3$). A toy log of four variants, the successor multisets its N-grams induce, and two generated shadow traces: a recombination of attested steps, and a Katz-consistent mutation ($e^{*}$) whose rate came from the resolved order-2 context and whose proposal came from the order-1 context}{figure.1.4}{}}
\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5}{\ignorespaces Katz backoff does the work twice (illustrative counts; activities abstracted). Step 1 resolves the deepest context with support, which supplies the next step and the Good--Turing novelty rate $\ensuremath  {p_{\mathit  {unseen}}}$ (Eq.\nobreakspace  {}\eqref  {eq:gt}). When the mutation fires, step 2 backs off one level further, to the deepest shorter context offering an activity unseen in the resolved one (Eq.\nobreakspace  {}\eqref  {eq:proposal}): the inserted $z$ is novel in the exact context, yet attested in a related shorter one.}}{12}{figure.1.5}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:mutation}{{5}{12}{Katz backoff does the work twice (illustrative counts; activities abstracted). Step 1 resolves the deepest context with support, which supplies the next step and the Good--Turing novelty rate $\punseen $ (Eq.~\eqref {eq:gt}). When the mutation fires, step 2 backs off one level further, to the deepest shorter context offering an activity unseen in the resolved one (Eq.~\eqref {eq:proposal}): the inserted $z$ is novel in the exact context, yet attested in a related shorter one}{figure.1.5}{}}
